# Task #131 (0.9.1-beta Smart Pro defect: GM root row missing while Tools -> Lodor worked):
# the root-entry heal now runs BEFORE the onboarding gate, so even a CANCELLED wizard
# session on an unconfigured pak leaves the root entry installed for the next boot scan.
desc Game Manager root entry heals even when the wizard is cancelled (unconfigured pak)
config none
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_config_absent
expect_file Emus/tg5040/LODORGM.pak/launch.sh
expect_file Roms/Game Manager (LODORGM)/Open Game Manager.gm
expect_file Roms/Game Manager (LODORGM)/Game Manager (LODORGM).m3u
expect_log gm root entry: Emus/tg5040/LODORGM.pak installed/refreshed
# task #134: legacy folder migrates away; NBSP bottom-sort alias lands in Roms/map.txt
sdfile+ Roms/0) Game Manager (LODORGM)/Open Game Manager.gm
expect_file_absent Roms/0) Game Manager (LODORGM)
expect_file_has Roms/map.txt	Game Manager (LODORGM)	 Game Manager
expect_log gm root entry: migrated - legacy Roms/0) Game Manager (LODORGM) removed
expect_log gm root entry: Roms/map.txt bottom-sort alias installed
